com.wordpress.loeper.kvv.base

Class TripRequestPrecise

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wordpress.loeper.kvv.base.TripRequest
      • com.wordpress.loeper.kvv.base.TripRequestPrecise

  • public class TripRequestPrecise
extends TripRequest
    A slightly more precise TripRequest which is needed if some station names are similar. This one cannot be constructed by the user manually, because the session values are obtained by the kvv server. This is why it can be obtained by AmbiguousTargetException.getModifiedTripRequest(TripSuggestion, TripSuggestion).
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Martin Löper
